import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from './pages/Home'
import Links from './pages/Links'

function RoutesApp(){
	<BrowserRouter>
		<Routes>
			<Route path="/" element={<Home/>} />
			<Route path="/links" element={<Links/>} />
		</Routes>
	</BrowserRouter>
}

export default RoutesApp;
